Package: LSTtools
Version: 0.0.2
Type: Package
Title: LSTtools: An R package to process thermal data derived from Landsat and MODIS images
Description: The LSTtools package provides 21 tools for the analysis of thermal data derived from Landsat and MODIS satellites. It includes a number of pre-processing, processing and post-processing functions to conduct Urban Heat Island (UHI) assessments. Quality filtering, data uncompression, spectral indices focused on green and grey urban infrastructure, hot-cold spot analysis and spatial statistics are included.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/RichardLemoine/LSTtools
